 like a white, cottony sea. Charred stumps of trees spoil the scene."

%message	2
"All of the trees and plants in this area have been burnt to stumps
 by the evil three-headed dragon!"

%message	3
"The ground is moist from the constant presence of clouds, but yet
 the trees are burnt and blackened."

%message	4
"The sky is blue and cloudless above this strange cloud land."

%message	5
"This is a very strange cloud land. There is just a bit of land dotted
 with charred trees encircled by a sea of white, fluffy clouds. This
 gives you the odd feeling of floating upon a cottony ocean. A cave
 entrance leads into a steep mountainside."

%message	6
"The mountain rises steeply from this bizarre cloud land.  A cave goes
 into its depths."

%message	7
"The mountain is unclimbable as it is much too steep and rocky."

%message	8
"It feels strangely hot up here."

%message	9
"The cave leads deep into the steep mountainside. Within, crumbly stone
 steps lead downward to murky depths." 

%message	10
"This mystical cloud land may never cease to amaze you, but..."

